{"article_id":"Kx7S5e0j9MN5eIQz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The opinions","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"expressed by columnists","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"are their own","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"and do not represent the views of .com .","depth":2},{"id":4,"text":"In baseball ,","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"when a team trades a player to another team","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"each side expects a benefit in return .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Not so in recent years","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"when it comes to trade agreements between the U.S. and other countries .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"President Trump has been right in his criticism of NAFTA and other trade deals","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"that have left the United States at a disadvantage ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"sidelining American goods ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"stifling job growth","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"and allowing other countries to steal America 's intellectual property .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"That has begun to change with a revamped NAFTA deal","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"the Trump administration named the USMCA ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"which stands for the U.S.-Mexico-Canada Agreement .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"At first , Mexico refused to alter its trade policies ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"but now it has .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau announced strong opposition","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"to making compromises","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"or changing what Trump said","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"was a tariff as high as `` 270 percent on U.S. dairy products . ''","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"However , hours before a midnight deadline , CNN reported ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"`` ... the U.S. and Canadian governments agreed to a deal","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that would allow U.S. farmers greater access to Canada 's dairy market","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"and address concerns about potential U.S. auto tariffs . ''","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"In May , even China ,","depth":14},{"id":28,"text":"which has been the most resistant of all","depth":15},{"id":29,"text":"in changing its unbalanced trade policy ,","depth":15},{"id":30,"text":"announced","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"it was cutting tariffs on imported cars and car parts .","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"More recently it pledged to soon reduce tariffs on a wide-range of consumer goods ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"including apparel , washing machines and makeup .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"As Bloomberg News reported ,","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"China 's announcement came","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"after the president `` decided to move ahead with additional tariffs on $ 50 billion of imports from China , a move","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"that could potentially derail the truce","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"reached last week between the world 's two biggest economies .","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"China hit back at that ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"with a foreign ministry spokeswoman saying on Wednesday","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"that China would respond accordingly","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"if the U.S. insisted on unilateral measures .","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"'' This is all part of the president 's negotiating strategy .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"It is unlikely China would have made its unilateral move on tariffs","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"had the president not campaigned about an unfair trade imbalance .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"At what turned into a news conference last Monday , the president said","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"he will deal with China later .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"His economic adviser Larry Kudlow told Fox Business Channel","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"`` ( USMCA ) sends an important message to China ...","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"North America is together .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"Nothing is imminent on China .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"I think","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"there 's discussions","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"going on . ''","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"Critics of President Trump have once again been proved wrong .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"President Obama and other Democrats said","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"manufacturing jobs were never coming back to America .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"They are .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"This is what the president said on Monday :","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"`` This is also a historic win for American manufacturers and American autoworkers ,","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"who have been treated so badly .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"We have lost so many jobs over the years under NAFTA .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"'' We are requiring a large portion of every car to be made by high-wage workers ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"which will greatly reduce foreign outsourcing ,","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"which was a tremendous problem ,","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"and means more auto parts and automobiles will be manufactured inside the United States . ''","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"He added :","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"`` Our companies wo n't be leaving the United States ,","depth":16},{"id":69,"text":"firing their workers","depth":17},{"id":70,"text":"and building their cars elsewhere .","depth":17},{"id":71,"text":"There is no longer that incentive .","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"It will form America back into a manufacturing powerhouse . ...","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"It will allow us to reclaim a supply chain","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"that has been offshored to the world","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"because of unfair trade issues .","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"This landmark agreement will send cash and jobs pouring into the United States and into North America . ...","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"Instead of jobs leaving for overseas ,","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"they will be returning back home . ''","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"The stock market loves it .","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"The Dow Jones rose nearly 280 points on Monday .","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"Democrats , like Senate Majority Leader Chuck Schumer , can only say","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"they want to see details .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"How do they oppose more jobs and higher wages for American workers ?","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"Past presidents of both parties have mostly bowed to globalists and other nations","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"that have put the interests of their countries first .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"President Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"starting with his campaign ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"promised to put American interests first ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"not to the detriment of other countries","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"-- they also are benefitting --","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"but to even out unfair deals","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"that have harmed America and Americans .","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"The best response to a policy","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"that is n't working , one","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"based on flawed ideology ,","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"is to embrace a policy","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"that works .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"The USMCA has the potential","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"to do great things for the U.S .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"There does n't seem to be a credible argument in opposition .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":201,"left":104,"right":200,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":103,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":102,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":108,"right":199,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":108,"left":106,"right":107,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":106,"left":4,"ri